image_frame = ImageFrame.read(self.image_path)
transformer = Pipeline([PixelBytesToMat(), Resize(256, 256), CenterCrop(224,
    224), ChannelNormalize(0.485, 0.456, 0.406, 0.229, 0.224, 0.225),
    MatToTensor(), ImageFrameToSample()])
transformed = transformer(image_frame)
transformed.get_sample()
